-- Lloyds to sell 38.5 percent stake in TSB at 260 pence/share
-- By Matt Scuffham
-- Thu Jun 19, 2014 03:35PM EDT
-- None



LONDON, June 19 (Reuters) - Lloyds Banking Group <LLOY.L> will on Friday announce the sale of a 38.5 percent stake in TSB and has priced the shares at 260 pence each, at the upper end of the expected range, sources familiar with the matter told Reuters on Thursday.

The sources said Lloyds had seen strong demand from institutional investors in Britain and the United States as well as from private retail investors. At least a quarter of the shares will be sold to the retail market.